   <text:p text:style-name="P2"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">Acknowledgments are due to J.C Tracetune CE pom ! The diagren showing the futility of attempting c measure compound value in terms one dimension</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">of</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">only , and to the National Bureau of Economie</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2"/>
