   <text:p text:style-name="P2"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">Comparing these two estimates we have the following, with a population of 104. 18 million :</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">Per Capita Income National Bureau Estimate. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .586 &quot; dollars &quot;</text:p>
