   <text:p text:style-name="P2">honesty, any right to add, subtract, multiply or divide the</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">dollars of two different days? We have not.? We have no more right than an astronomer would have to multiply feet by</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">metres indiscriminately and then identify his comet with the aid of astronomical finesse.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2"/>
